{
  "stem": "5891.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And out in the fields, too, mowing the grass and everything.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In those days, they didn't have all this machinery stuff.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They had those [GERMAN], you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I don't know what they call that here in America.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Cut the grass with, you know, with-- we called it a [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There's like a hand stick on it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's like a [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What they called it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that [GERMAN] went in her leg, and she cut her ankle on that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So she had to be hospitalized, and they took her to Marburg, 33 kilometers from Biedenkopf.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we used to go visit her on the bikes, 33 kilometers gone, and 33 kilo-- there was no problem at all.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Those days, that's how we-- that's all we knew.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, no fancy buses and fancy this and that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But-- this-- and it was-- we done this.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If you say today, 33 kilometers gone, and 66 kilometers on a bike?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know what I mean?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was a daily routine, really.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I don't know how I got to talk about that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You were telling me about the wagons and the bikes.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, so there was no-- you know, if the wagon, if my dad was-- sometimes my dad was hired for doing the fieldwork, like plowing their fields, because we had the horses and the equipment.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So my dad did that kind of work, also.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now, of course, the bigger girls or the boys was around, had to help.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Drive the horses, or he loaded up the wagons.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And you know, 13, 12, no matter what age you were, if you were capable of doing it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we wanted to do all this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This was something-- because we were always together.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We took our lunches with us, then.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[GERMAN] and [GERMAN] and [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
